ED_Title: The situation in the temporarily occupied territories of Ukraine
ED_DecisionText: At its 107th plenary meeting, on 16 September 2019, the General Assembly, by a recorded vote of 65 to 17, with 54 abstentions,  decided to include the item entitled “The situation in the temporarily occupied territories of Ukraine” in the draft agenda of its seventy-fourth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
